"{\"uid\": \"tmz.com-2024-07-26-2024-paris-olympics-police-crackdown-on-prostitution\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"With an influx of visitors heading to Paris for the 2024 Olympics, French police are cracking down on prostitution ... and we have learned an anti-pimping brigade is even leading the charge.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 190, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 38, \"end\": 43, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999958847638, \"rank\": 4.1152247633054e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 67, \"end\": 80, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4657711589519757e-27, \"text\": \"French police\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Press Office for the Police Prefecture tells TMZ ... authorities are doing what they can to combat illegal sex work in the City of Lights.\", \"from\": 192, \"to\": 334, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are told checkpoints and other road operations are targeted to try and put a stop to pimping in the Bois de Vincennes, Bois de Boulogne and Belleville sectors.\", \"from\": 335, \"to\": 497, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 457, \"end\": 473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bois_de_Boulogne\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bois de Boulogne\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bois_de_Boulogne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bois_de_Boulogne\"}, {\"begin\": 478, \"end\": 488, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belleville,_Ontario\", \"score\": 0.5795018015811559, \"rank\": 0.36195615151566973, \"text\": \"Belleville\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belleville,_Ontario\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belleville,_Ontario\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A formal brigade -- known as the BRP -- has even formed ... and we are told they will make their presence seriously known in the area.\", \"from\": 499, \"to\": 633, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 532, \"end\": 535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bombardier_Recreational_Products\", \"score\": 0.999948813654039, \"rank\": 4.947020135297836e-05, \"text\": \"BRP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bombardier_Recreational_Products\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bombardier_Recreational_Products\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is also a group in charge of surveilling night establishments, such as cabarets ... where anti-sex work laws will be reinforced.\", \"from\": 634, \"to\": 768, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The City of Paris and the Public Prosecutor's Office are also assisting in the crackdown, as they have collaborated to bring about prevention and awareness measures.\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 935, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 782, \"end\": 787, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999958847638, \"rank\": 4.1152247633054e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 796, \"end\": 813, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prosecutor\", \"score\": 0.9999999986150669, \"rank\": 1.3850126547121772e-09, \"text\": \"Public Prosecutor\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prosecutor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prosecutor\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While this increase in police presence may be a relief to residents and tourists, several nonprofit organizations spoke out on behalf of sex workers ahead of the Olympics ... as they believe the \\\"repression first\\\" mindset has a negative impact on the sex workers' health and safety.\", \"from\": 937, \"to\": 1219, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"PerFrance 24, charity groups implored authorities to focus less on targeting sex workers and, instead, take down the \\\"criminal organizations which rob, rape and assault them.\\\"\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1396, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The orgs also defended that sex workers are not flocking to Paris amid the Olympics, as accommodations have become too expensive for them to reside there.\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1552, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1458, \"end\": 1463, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999958847638, \"rank\": 4.1152247633054e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This update comes a year after activists pushed back at anti-prostitution efforts in France, saying new measures risked putting sex workers in great peril.\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1709, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1639, \"end\": 1645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.703812660183654, \"rank\": 0.3642918525279556, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ICYMI ... France officially outlawed brothels in 1946, but made paying someone for sex illegal in 2016 -- an effort to punish the client instead of the worker.\", \"from\": 1711, \"to\": 1870, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1721, \"end\": 1727, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.703812660183654, \"rank\": 0.3642918525279556, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet, more pressure means more hiding ... which does nothing for the sex workers' safety.\", \"from\": 1872, \"to\": 1960, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sounds like the crackdown may be a bit counterproductive.\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 2019, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yes!\", \"from\": 2021, \"to\": 2025, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Send me email updates and offers from TMZ and its Affiliates.\", \"from\": 2026, \"to\": 2087, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2064, \"end\": 2067, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TMZ\", \"score\": 0.9999999985541308, \"rank\": 1.445878036023048e-09, \"text\": \"TMZ\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TMZ\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TMZ\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By subscribing, I agree to thePrivacy PolicyandTerms of Use\", \"from\": 2088, \"to\": 2147, \"entities\": []}]}"